caption: Delicious!!!! I'm not usually a fan of vegan meat but they made thiers taste AMAZING. Everything they make is delicious. Everything hits your taste buds just right. The burger, the subs, the fried rolls, the beverages, everything! DCAC Eatz is a great black owned business and has that great black owned business flavor. It's vegan, but it's still delicious! I recommend this to everyone looking for something tasty.

LET ME BE CLEAR... BEST VEGAN BURGER I EVER HAD.... stopped by the Vegan festival and had a chance to talk with them and hear their story so me and the crew tried some stuff. The Vegan Burger delicious as well as the CHIK something salad sandwich... THEY ARE A LITTLE PRICEY 15.00 for the burger and thats the only reason for the 4 stars. but well worth it. I meant to take a pic but it was sooo good i demolished it quickly
